    dc:creator "Young, Daniel K." ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Sundapyrochroa: A new genus of Fire-Colored Beetles (Coleoptera: Pyrochroidae: Pyrochroinae) from the Sunda Shelf, with a key to the three species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178676>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178678>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178682>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178680>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178684>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178686>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178688> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178676>
    dc:description "Figures 1–3. Sundapyrochroa atricolor (Pic). 1) Habitus, adult male, dorsal. 2) Left antenna, lateroventral. 3) Habitus, adult female, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178678>
    dc:description "Figures 4–6. Sundapyrochroa nigripennis (Pic). 4) Habitus, adult male, dorsal. 5) Habitus, melanic adult male, dorsal. 6) Habitus, adult female, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178678/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178682>
    dc:description "Figures 9-10. Sundapyrochroa sumatrensis (Pic), habitus adult male illustrating color variations." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178682/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178680>
    dc:description "Figures 7–8. Sundapyrochroa nigripennis (Pic). 7) Head, adult male, dorsal. 8) Left antenna, dorsolateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178680/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178684>
    dc:description "Figures 11–12. Sundapyrochroa sumatrensis (Pic). 11) Head, adult male, dorsal. 12) Habitus, adult female, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178684/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178686>
    dc:description "Figures 13–21. Three species of Sundapyrochroa. 13) S. atricolor (Pic), abdominal sternite eight. 14) S. atricolor (Pic), tegmen, dorsal. 15) S. atricolor (Pic), penis, dorsal. 16) S. nigripennis (Pic), abdominal sternite eight. 17) S. nigripennis (Pic), tegmen, dorsal. 18) S. nigripennis (Pic), penis, dorsal. 19) S. sumatrensis (Pic), abdominal sternite eight. 20) S. sumatrensis (Pic), tegmen, dorsal. 21) S. sumatrensis (Pic), penis, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178686/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178688>
    dc:description "Figures 22–23. Two species of Pyrochroidae. 22) Dendroides canadensis Latreille, habitus adult male, dorsal. 23) Sinodendroides chinensis Young, habitus adult male, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178688/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

